title: Duke Nukem 2 playthrough -- Part 1
description: This game is 100x harder than the first one and much more annoying, although the music and graphics are better so that's cool. Took me 3 hours to get through the first two episodes. Will probably take even longer to get through 3 and 4, but I think I'm going to play them on easy to save my remaining sanity.
